'''Samet Akaydın''' (born 13 March 1994) is a Turkish professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Süper Lig]] club [[Çaykur Rizespor]] and the [[Turkey national football team|Turkey national team]].

==Club career==
Akaydın began his youth career with [[Black Sea Region]]-based clubs [[Trabzon İdmanocağı]], [[Trabzonspor U21|Trabzonspor]], [[Boluspor]] and started his professional career with hometown club [[Arsinspor]]. He played four seasons with [[Istanbul]]-based club [[Sancaktepe FK|Sancaktepe]], one season with [[Şanlıurfaspor]], one and a half seasons with [[Ankara Keçiörengücü S.K.|Ankara Keçiörengücü]].{{citation needed|date=February 2026}}

===Adana Demirspor===
Akaydın moved to [[Süper Lig]] side [[Adana Demirspor]] until the end of the 2023-24 season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ntvspor.net/futbol/samet-akaydin-adana-demirspor-da-60087ec3560350042c6abc22|title=Samet Akaydın, Adana Demirspor'da|publisher=NtvSpor.net|date=20 January 2021}}</ref> On 23 January 2021, he made his debut against [[Bursaspor]]. On 18 September 2021, he made his Süper Lig debut against [[Rizespor]] in a 3–1 win.{{citation needed|date=February 2026}}

He made 49 Süper Lig (with 4 goals) and 6 [[TFF First League]] appearances with the team and also made three [[Turkish cup]] appearances and one goal. He was selected to the [[Turkey national football team|national team]].{{citation needed|date=February 2026}}

===Fenerbahçe===
On 4 December 2023, Akaydın signed Turkish powerhouse [[Fenerbahçe S.K. (football)|Fenerbahçe]], until the end of the 2026–27 season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fenerbahce.org/haberler/futbol/2023/1/ailemize-hos-geldin-samet-akaydin|title=Ailemize hoş geldin Samet Akaydın|publisher=Fenerbahçe SK|date=12 January 2023}}</ref> He made his Süper Lig debut for the team in a 2–1 away game win over [[Gaziantep FK]] on 15 January 2023.{{citation needed|date=February 2026}}

On 9 March 2023, he made his continental debut in the [[UEFA Europa League]] [[2022–23 UEFA Europa League knockout phase#Round of 16|round of 16]] match against [[Sevilla FC|Sevilla]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fenerbahce.org/haberler/futbol/2023/3/sevilla-2-0-fenerbahce|title=Sevilla 2-0 Fenerbahçe|publisher=Fenerbahçe SK|date=9 March 2023}}</ref>

On 10 November 2024, he scored his first goal with the team against [[Sivasspor]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fenerbahce.org/haberler/futbol/2024/11/fenerbahce-4-0-net-global-sivasspor|title=Fenerbahçe 4-0 Net Global Sivasspor|publisher=Fenerbahçe SK|date=10 November 2024}}</ref>

====Panathinaikos (loan)====
On 14 January 2024, Akaydin joined Greek side [[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]] on loan from Fenerbahçe, until the end of the [[2023–24 Panathinaikos F.C. season|2023–24 season]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pao.gr/transfers/ston-panathinaiko-o-samet-akaintin/ |title=Στον Παναθηναϊκό ο Σαμέτ Ακαϊντίν |date=14 January 2024 |publisher=Panathinaikos FC|access-date=14 January 2024 |language=el}}</ref>

He was excluded from the squad due to his [[Mustafa Kemal Atatürk]] social media post for [[Commemoration of Atatürk, Youth and Sports Day]] on 19 May 2024. Panathinaikos asked him to remove his post but he didn't accept the club's request and did not remove the post, then he was excluded from the main squad. Akaydın, who informed Fenerbahçe that he wanted to leave Panathinaikos after what happened, decided to return to Turkey.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.goal.com/tr/haber/19-mayis-paylasimi-yapan-samet-akaydin-kadro-disi-birakildi/bltb665147f6cf09d48|title=19 Mayıs paylaşımı yapan Samet Akaydin kadro dışı bırakıldı|publisher=GOAL.com|date=20 May 2024}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.milliyet.com.tr/skorer/yunanistanda-skandal-samet-akaydin-karari-ataturk-paylasimi-sonrasu-kadro-disi-7129640|title=Yunanistan'da skandal Samet Akaydin kararı! Atatürk paylaşımı sonrası kadro dışı|publisher=Milliyet|date=20 May 2024}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/panathinaikostan-19-mayis-ayibi-samet-akaydinden-paylasimini-kaldirmasini-isteyip-kadro-disi-biraktilar-42464603|title=Panathinaikos'tan 19 Mayıs ayıbı! Samet Akaydin'den paylaşımını kaldırmasını isteyip, kadro dışı bıraktılar...|publisher=Hürriyet|date=20 May 2024}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fanatik.com.tr/fenerbahce/son-dakika-panathinaikostan-skandal-hareket-samet-akaydin-ataturk-paylasimi-nedeniyle-kadro-disi-kaldi-2548092|title=Panathinaikos'tan skandal hareket: Samet Akaydin, Atatürk paylaşımı nedeniyle kadro dışı kaldı|publisher=Fanatik|date=20 May 2024}}</ref>

==International career==
Akaydın debuted with the [[Turkey national football team|Turkey national team]] in a friendly 2–1 win over the [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic]] on 19 November 2022.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cablefreetv.org/tayyip-talha-sanuc-samet-akaydin-and-onur-bulut-spoke-after-the-czechia-match/|title=Tayyip Talha Sanuç, Samet Akaydin and Onur Bulut spoke after the Czechia match!|date=19 November 2022|access-date=23 November 2022|archive-date=23 November 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221123202048/https://cablefreetv.org/tayyip-talha-sanuc-samet-akaydin-and-onur-bulut-spoke-after-the-czechia-match/|url-status=dead}}</ref>

Akaydın was selected to represent his nation at the [[UEFA Euro 2024]].<ref>{{cite news |date=7 June 2024 |title=A Millî Takımımızın EURO 2024 Aday Kadrosu Açıklandı |trans-title=EURO 2024 Candidate Squad of Our National Team Announced |url=https://www.tff.org/default.aspx?pageID=202&ftxtID=44561 |language=tr |publisher=Turkish Football Federation |access-date=7 June 2024}}</ref> Notably, he scored an [[own goal]] past [[Altay Bayındır]] from outside the box in the nation's 3–0 loss to [[Portugal national football team|Portugal]] during the group stage.<ref>{{cite web |last=Tobin |first=Sam |date=23 June 2024 |title=Portugal coast into Euro 2024 last-16 with 3-0 victory over Turkey |url=https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/portugal-coast-into-euro-2024-last-16-with-3-0-victory-over-turkey-2024-06-22/ |access-date=September 4, 2024 |publisher=Reuters}}</ref> On 6 July, he scored his first international goal, by opening the score in a 2–1 defeat against the [[Netherlands national football team|Netherlands]] in the quarter-final of the competition.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/match/2036207/ |title=Netherlands 2–1 Türkiye |publisher=UEFA |date=6 July 2024 }}</ref>

==Style of play==
Akaydın is a quick, aggressive, physically strong, and tenacious defender, who was known for his work-rate, energy, and hard-tackling style of play. Due to his height, he was also an aerial threat on [[Set piece (football)|set-pieces]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tff.org/default.aspx?pageID=286&ftxtID=38459 |title=Samet Akaydın: "Futboldan başka bir şey düşünmüyorum" |publisher=TFF.org |date=1 September 2022 }}</ref>

